'''Charging Wampa''' was a [[Teräs Käsi/Legends|Teräs Käsi]] move, named after the [[Wampa/Legends|Wampa]] of [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]. The move involved charging at one's opponent, attempting to hit them in the jaw, followed by a simultaneous hit of both arms on the opponent's neck.

